bloodworms.description:
• Minimum fish tier: **A**
• Catches exclusively: **small** fish
• More likely to catch: **panfish**

bread.description:
• Minimum fish tier: **C**
• Catches exclusively: **small** fish
• More likely to catch: **minnow**

crab.description:
• Minimum fish tier: **B**
• Catches exclusively: **large** & **extra large** fish

dragonfly.description:
• Minimum fish tier: **C**
• Catches exclusively: **large**, **extra large** fish
• More likely to catch: **carp**

large_cutbait.description:
• Minimum fish tier: **S**
• Catches exclusively: **large** & **extra large** fish
• More likely to catch: **sturgeon**

leeches.description:
• Minimum fish tier: **B**
• Catches exclusively: **medium**, **large** & **extra large** fish
• More likely to catch: **perch**

medium_cutbait.description:
• Minimum fish tier: **S**
• Catches exclusively: **medium**, **large** & **extra large** fish
• More likely to catch: **gar**

minnows.description:
• Catches exclusively **small**, **medium** & **large** fish
• More likely to catch: **trout** & **crappie**

sardine.description:
• Minimum fish tier: **B**
• Catches exclusively **medium** & **large** fish
• More likely to catch: **bass**

shrimp.description:
• Minimum fish tier: **A**
• Catches exclusively: **medium**, **large** & **extra large** fish
• More likely to catch: **catfish** & **pike**

small_cutbait.description:
• Minimum fish tier: **S**
• More likely to catch: **catfish**
